        "description": "Retrospective and prospective observational data collection from 12 clinical sites. Pump operating parameters, blood flow rates, and hemolysis index measurements were recorded under routine clinical use without experimental manipulation of variables. Data were aggregated and compared to CFD predictions post hoc.",
